headline: Cisco Systems, Inc. (CSCO) Joins Stargate UAE Consortium to Build AI Data Center
summary: On May 22, Cisco Systems, Inc. (NASDAQ:CSCO) announced it would join technology giants, including Nvidia, OpenAI, and Oracle, to build a sweeping AI campus in the UAE under the Stargate project announced during President Trump’s recent visit to the country. The project aims to build the largest set of AI data centers outside the U.S. […]
